		{
			"id":"workflow-description",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"🎯 工作流设计原则\n\n1. 明确目标 → 选择合适的AI工具\n2. 工具组合 → 发挥各自优势\n3. 数据流转 → 确保兼容性\n4. 持续优化 → 迭代改进",
			"styleAttributes":{"backgroundColor":"#2d3748","textColor":"#a0aec0","fontSize":"12","textAlign":"left","borderColor":"#4a5568","borderWidth":"2"},
			"x":-600,
			"y":400,
			"width":400,
			"height":150
		},
		{
			"id":"integration-note",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"💡 集成建议\n\n• API优先：选择支持API的工具\n• 数据格式：统一使用JSON\n• 错误处理：完善的异常机制\n• 监控日志：记录关键节点",
			"styleAttributes":{"backgroundColor":"#1a365d","textColor":"#cbd5e0","fontSize":"12","textAlign":"left","borderColor":"#2b6cb0","borderWidth":"2"},
			"x":-100,
			"y":400,
			"width":350,
			"height":150
		}
